text: "In da Club" is a 2003 song by American rapper 50 Cent and is the lead single from his debut studio album Get Rich or Die Tryin'. It topped the single charts in Australia, Canada, Denmark, Germany, Ireland, New Zealand, Switzerland and the United States. It went to the top ten in Austria, Belgium, Finland, Greece, Italy, the Netherlands, Norway, Romania, Scotland, Sweden and the United Kingdom. It also went to number 16 in France. The song was nominated for 2 Grammy Awards in 2004, but lost to Eminem's song "Lose Yourself".46th "Grammy Awards - 2004". Rock on the Net. Retrieved July 5, 2007.
